    "body" : "<p>Easiest method: <code>Alt</code>+<code>Enter</code> on</p>\n\n<pre><code>private static final long serialVersionUID = ;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>IntelliJ will underline the space after the <code>=</code>. put your cursor on it and hit <code>alt</code>+<code>Enter</code> (<code>Option</code>+<code>Enter</code> on Mac). You'll get a popover that says \"Randomly Change serialVersionUID Initializer\". Just hit enter, and it'll populate that space with a random long. </p>\n"
